    <title>Re: CloudEvents at SAP 🌁</title>
    <updated>2024-06-17T17:59:50.172000+02:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>ajmaradiaga</name>
      <uri>https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/107</uri>
    </author>
    <content>&lt;P&gt;&lt;a href="https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/1446169"&gt;@Lidia-Sarasua&lt;/a&gt;, a public EDA strategy document is in the works, and that should help you highlight the differences and help decide which one to select.&lt;/P&gt;</content>
    <link href="https://community.sap.com/t5/application-development-blog-posts/cloudevents-at-sap/bc-p/13733535#M48374"/>
    <published>2024-06-17T17:59:50.172000+02:00</published>
