    <content>&lt;DIV class=""&gt;&lt;P&gt;The local &lt;STRONG&gt;SAP Community in Santiago&lt;/STRONG&gt; has a chance to meet after our first of two local SAP CodeJams!&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;SAP Stammtisch in Santiago&lt;/STRONG&gt; will happen&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;on&amp;nbsp;August 12th, 2024 at 18:00 CLT &lt;/STRONG&gt;for a few hours, so join us and be a part of our Group!&amp;nbsp; &lt;U&gt;You don't have to be an attendee of our SAP CodeJam events&lt;/U&gt;, just someone active or curious about the SAP Community and our focus on #developers&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;Let’s talk about what's new in the SAP world, about interesting SAP projects in the region, and what's new with ourselves.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Please let us know if you will participate in SAP Stammtisch by clicking "I will attend", &lt;EM&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;we have a table reservation for 12&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/EM&gt; at the Fuente Chilena.&amp;nbsp; FYI, everyone is responsible for their own to buy a food/drink item if they wish, we are just happy for the chance to connect in person and have some relaxing conversation!&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;Click here to find more information about the &lt;A href="https://community.sap.com/t5/sap-codejam-blog-posts/sap-codejam-roadshow-2024-latin-america-edition-august-8th-21st-2024/ba-p/13710015" target="_self"&gt;SAP Developer Advocates Latin America Roadshow&lt;/A&gt; &lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;DIV class=""&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;</content>
